Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:22.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love is such a sweet illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.66,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's come together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:27.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can't seem to stop my imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.34,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Goes on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:33.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}What a ridiculous situation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.06,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Another matter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:40.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But I can't deny，I'm faced with a tricky temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:45.90,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}In the world that keeps on changing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:51.16,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't know why my heart is aching
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:04:00.31,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Gotta handle it，no more hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:03.32,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There can be no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.48,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:07.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“My mind is as free as the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.56,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But now what I should do is to fall in love”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.74,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“I don't need that kind of real things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:18.01,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Feels like I'm lost in the labyrinth”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.18,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:22.03,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“There must be the meaning of life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:25.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Somehow unexpected happenings thrill me”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.60,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}God only knows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“Just believe in myself and my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:32.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Anyone could be a hero and heroine”
